      • Token

        public Token(Token.Kind k,
             int c,
             java.lang.String t)
        This fully parameterized constructor is used to establish each lexical token. There is no default constructor defined because this class is completely determined by the Lexer Class
        Parameters:
        k - - This specifies the Kind of the token using the above enumeration
        c - - This code provides detail about an element of a particular token Kind
        t - - This String specifies the actual textual representation of the token
